<element xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
         xmlns:zenta="http://magwas.rulez.org/zenta"
         xsi:type="zenta:BasicObject"
         name="exception handling"
         id="906f88cc-7dab-4e27-a2b0-92058eed3965"
         ancestor="behaviour">
   <documentation>All exceptions explicitly thrown are converter to appropriate error messages.

The exceptions are turned into error messages by RestResponseEntityExceptionHandler in the following way:

NotLoggedInException : unauthorized
UnauthorizedException: unauthorized
ValidationException: bad request
NotFoundException: not found
other exceptions: 500

The exception and message is logged by RestResponseEntityExceptionHandler
</documentation>
</element>
